    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 1 requirements. CFD predictions of NIH agree with experimental measurements within 9.4% across all operating points, and worst-case RH = 0.87 satisfies the RH < 1 acceptance criterion. The model is deemed credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Decision: Accepted.",
